# ‡∏õ‡πâ‡∏≠‡∏á‡∏Å‡∏±‡∏ô‡∏Å‡∏≤‡∏£ cache ‡πÑ‡∏ü‡∏•‡πå CSS ‡πÅ‡∏•‡∏∞ JavaScript
<FilesMatch "\.(css|js)$">
    Header set Cache-Control "no-cache, no-store, must-revalidate"
    Header set Pragma "no-cache"
    Header set Expires 0
</FilesMatch>

# ‡∏õ‡πâ‡∏≠‡∏á‡∏Å‡∏±‡∏ô‡∏Å‡∏≤‡∏£ cache ‡πÑ‡∏ü‡∏•‡πå HTML
<FilesMatch "\.(html|htm)$">
    Header set Cache-Control "no-cache, no-store, must-revalidate"
    Header set Pragma "no-cache"
    Header set Expires 0
</FilesMatch>

# ‡πÄ‡∏û‡∏¥‡πà‡∏° version parameter ‡πÉ‡∏´‡πâ‡∏Å‡∏±‡∏ö‡πÑ‡∏ü‡∏•‡πå CSS ‡πÅ‡∏•‡∏∞ JS
RewriteEngine On
RewriteCond %{REQUEST_FILENAME} -f
RewriteRule ^(.+)\.(css|js)$ $1.$2?v=%{TIME} [L]

# ‡∏õ‡πâ‡∏≠‡∏á‡∏Å‡∏±‡∏ô‡∏Å‡∏≤‡∏£ cache ‡∏£‡∏π‡∏õ‡∏†‡∏≤‡∏û
<FilesMatch "\.(jpg|jpeg|png|gif|webp|avif)$">
